00:33:22,456 --> 00:33:27,369
Each of these tubes has
a so-called <i>PINI extraction system</i>,

535
00:33:27,369 --> 00:33:29,212
that's a Plug-in Neutral Injector.

536
00:33:29,212 --> 00:33:33,184
This particular technology
was developed for JET.

537
00:33:33,184 --> 00:33:36,696
We can notice the electromagnet

538
00:33:36,696 --> 00:33:41,135
to deflect the non-neutralized ions,

539
00:33:41,135 --> 00:33:45,885
the dump for those that in fact
need to be evacuated

540
00:33:45,885 --> 00:33:47,789
because they're not neutral.

541
00:33:47,789 --> 00:33:51,576
And the calorimeter that measures
how much power we are actually injecting.

542
00:33:51,576 --> 00:33:56,839
On this side there would be a port
