00:34:08,605 --> 00:34:12,207
for a height of about 80 cm.

547
00:34:12,881 --> 00:34:17,576
I just put the picture because
I'd like to stress the point that

548
00:34:17,576 --> 00:34:20,010
the divergence of the beam
is an important parameter.

549
00:34:20,010 --> 00:34:25,582
We can't impinge with the beam
on the walls of the duct

550
00:34:25,582 --> 00:34:27,753
that takes us to the machine,

551
00:34:28,144 --> 00:34:30,857
both because we would damage
the beam duct,

552
00:34:30,857 --> 00:34:33,666
but also because as soon as
we deposit some power here

553
00:34:33,666 --> 00:34:38,915
there will be significant outgassing
from the beam wall interactions,

554
00:34:38,915 --> 00:34:41,769
and this outgassing would block
the propagation of the beam,

555
00:34:41,769 --> 00:34:46,664
which would therefore never even
reach the plasma volume.

556
00:34:46,949 --> 00:34:49,447
So we said that
the beam works by generating

557
00:34:50,344 --> 00:34:52,131
fast neutrals that become fast ions.

558
00:34:52,131 --> 00:34:55,498
Let's look at the evidence
for the presence of these fast ions

559
00:34:55,498 --> 00:34:59,618
in a JET tokamak in a few examples.

