561
00:35:05,935 --> 00:35:08,536
using what we call tritium NBI <i>blips</i>,

562
00:35:08,536 --> 00:35:11,538
so small amounts of tritium

563
00:35:11,538 --> 00:35:15,268
injected in the NBI system.

