00:36:00,516 --> 00:36:02,188
we can have slightly different profiles,

579
00:36:02,188 --> 00:36:06,087
or in fact significantly different
profiles for the fast ions.

580
00:36:06,087 --> 00:36:09,738
So this confirms
that we are actually injecting

581
00:36:09,738 --> 00:36:14,559
the fast ions into the plasma
where we think they are going,

582
00:36:14,559 --> 00:36:20,024
[and in this case] Let me now just say
a few words about the NBI system

583
00:36:20,024 --> 00:36:23,699
that's being designed
and constructed for ITER.

584
00:36:23,699 --> 00:36:26,397
For heating and current drive,

585
00:36:27,212 --> 00:36:29,631
we will have two, at least initially,

586
00:36:29,631 --> 00:36:33,669
two tangential beams
of negative ions, deuterium.

587
00:36:34,782 --> 00:36:40,163
Because of the size of ITER,
these would be in the MeV range

588
00:36:40,163 --> 00:36:43,601
for the energy,
in fact would be about 1MeV,

589
00:36:44,347 --> 00:36:46,580
a power of 33MW,

590
00:36:47,841 --> 00:36:49,209
similar to that of JET,

591
00:36:49,209 --> 00:36:51,491
but for much longer duration of a pulse,

592
00:36:52,112 --> 00:36:54,786
3,600 seconds.

593
00:36:55,289 --> 00:36:59,213
There will also be a third beam,
